	<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 35pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=center><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 华文中宋; FONT-SIZE: 22pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">昆山市经信委</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 华文中宋" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 华文中宋; FONT-SIZE: 22pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年政府信息公开工作年度报告</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 华文中宋" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">根据《政府信息公开条例》、《关于全面推进政务公开工作的实施意见》、《昆山市</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">年政务公开工作要点》等文件精神，编制本报告。统计数据时间段从</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">年</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">月</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">日起至</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">年</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>12</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">月</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>31</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">日止。本报告全文包括概述、主动公开政府信息情况、政府信息依申请公开办理情况、政府信息公开的收费及减免情况、因政府信息公开申请行政复议、提起诉讼的情况、政府信息公开工作存在的主要问题及改进措施。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">可在中国昆山网经济和信息化委员会部门信息公开专栏下载电子版报告。如对本报告有任何疑问，可与昆山市经信委办公室联系，联系电话：</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>0512-57314939</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">，电子邮箱：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="undefined/mailto:ksjxw_bgs@163.com"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-ansi-font-size: 16.0pt"><FONT color=#0000ff>ksjxw_bgs@163.com</FONT></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">一、概况</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">今年以来，我委</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; BACKGROUND: white; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">立足服务企业、服务基层、服务群众，不断提高政府信息公开质量水平，努力提高经信委部门工作的透明度、公信力，政府信息公开工作取得一定成效。</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: white; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">、完善网站信息公开管理规章制度。我委门户网站于去年</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">月关闭并将相关内容于中国昆山网站部门动态专栏统一发布。为维护专栏信息的及时发布，我委及时完善了网站信息公开管理的相关制度，分管领导负总责，办公室人员具体负责网站信息的发布和管理。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">、修订完善了网站管理内容保障机制、加强信息发布审核和保密工作。完善对网站信息的监控与管理，上网信息严格按程序审批，重要数据资料进行备份，采取严格的防范措施，确保网络公开信息的及时性和精准性。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">二、主动公开政府信息情况</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">我委本年度主动公开政府信息共</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>266</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">条，其中全文电子化达</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>100%</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">在主动公开的信息中，政策法规类信息</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>0 </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">条；规划计划类信息</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">条，占总体的比例为</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>0.38% </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">；业务类信息</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>261</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">条，其中包括委内各类文件、年度重点工作安排和工作总结等，占总体比例为</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>98.1%</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">；政府信息公开年度报告</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">条；占总体的比例为</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>0.38%</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">，机构领导及分工类信息</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">条，占总体的比例为</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>1.13%</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">三、政府信息依申请公开办理情况</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">我委按规定，将</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">昆山市经信委信息公开申请表及昆山市经信委信息公开申请流程图等内容及时上网公开，一年来，未收到任何形式的申请。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">四、政府信息公开的收费及减免情况</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">一年来，我委公开的相关网上信息均为免费阅览，不收取任何费用。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">五、因政府信息公开申请行政复议、提起行政诉讼的情况</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">我委</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年度未发生针对本部门有关政府信息公开事务的行政复议案、行政诉讼案。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">六、政府信息公开工作存在的主要问题及改进措施</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">年的政府信息公开工作还存在如下不足：一是主动公开的信息在网站上公开发布的及时性、规范性有待进一步加强；二是政府信息公开工作的操作流程有待进一步改善；三是行政权力网上公开透明运行工作有待进一步深化。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">年，我委政府信息公开工作将进一步在抓深入、抓规范、抓实效上下功夫，以公开促服务，以服务树形象，推动我委信息公开工作再上新台阶。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">、凝聚共识，提高政府信息公开意识</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">我委将按照政府信息公开工作要求，认真开展自查自纠，全面提高我委信息公开工作的水平。按照行政工作不同业务特点，建设面向公众、方便获取、形式多样的政府信息公开载体，扩展公开渠道，推进政府信息公开进企业，扩大政府信息公开的社会影响力。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">、完善制度，提高政府信息公开水平</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">我委将</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">制订委内信息工作考核办法，充分调动全体人员搜集、撰写、报送及公开信息的积极性、主动性和自觉性，最大范围、最广深度获取应公开及可公开的各类信息。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">定期邀请专业人员对全委工作人员进行信息收集、整合、撰写等方面开展业务培训，提高全委人员信息工作意识和能力。进一步规范开展网站信息公开工作，严格按照</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">以公开为原则，以不公开为例外</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">、</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">上网信息不涉密、涉密信息不上网</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">的要求，全面梳理信息，严格信息审核和发布，主动公开和依申请公开政府信息，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">确保应该公开内容全部公开，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">保证公开信息的完整性和准确性。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt">、整合资源，提高政府信息公开效率</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">采取积极有效方式，拓宽我委政府信息公开渠道，在完善政府网站信息公开专栏作为政府信息公开第一平台的基础上，进一步创新公开方式、扩大公开内容和范围。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">加大督办力度，做好分类公开的各项工作，及时公布信息，切实做到信息公开的内容常换常新，并确保公开信息质量。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">将政府信息公开工作更好地融入日常业务工作，确保政务信息及时、准确、规范的对外公开。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 10pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
